  "original_title": "Fuel for school vans from SLTB depots from today: President",
  "text_idx": {
    "en": {
      "title": "Fuel for school vans from SLTB depots from today: President",
      "author": "unknown",
      "body_lines": [
        "COLOMBO (News 1st); President Ranil Wickremesinghe has instructed to streamline and expedite the fuel distribution process, during a meeting held at the Prime Minister\u2019s office today (23).",
        "The President had also instructed the Minister of Transport to enable school vans to obtain fuel from SLTB depots from 03:00 PM today, in view of the reopening of schools from 25th of July.",
        "Moreover, the President also instructed to issue fuel from SLTB depots and Army camps for fisheries, tourism and agriculture sectors, while he also instructed authorities to take swift action against fuel hoarders.",
        "Govt and Govt approved private schools to resume activities on 25th July"
      ],
